        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 一 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>乾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>乾：元，亨，利，貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：潛龍，勿用。\n九二：見龍在田，利見大人。\n九三：君子終日乾乾，夕惕，若厲，無咎。\n九四：或躍在淵，無咎。\n九五：飛龍在天，利見大人。\n上九：亢龍有悔。\n用九：見群龍無首，吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：大哉乾元，萬物資始，乃統天。雲行雨施，品物流形。\n　　　大明終始，六位時成，時乘六龍以御天。\n　　　乾道變化，各正性命，保合太和，乃利貞。首出庶物，萬國咸寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">象曰：天行健，君子以自強不息。\n　　　潛龍勿用，陽在下也。\n　　　見龍在田，德施普也。\n　　　終日乾乾，反復道也。\n　　　或躍在淵，進無咎也。\n　　　飛龍在天，大人造也。\n　　　亢龍有悔，盈不可久也。\n　　　用九，天德不可為首也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">文言曰：「元者，善之長也，亨者，嘉之會也，利者，義之和也，貞者，事之幹也。\n　　　　　君子體仁，足以長人；嘉會，足以合禮；利物，足以和義；貞固，足以幹事。\n　　　　　君子行此四德，故曰：乾：元亨利貞。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九曰：「潛龍勿用。」何謂也？\n子曰：「龍德而隱者也。不易乎世，不成乎名；遯世無悶，不見是而無悶；\n　　　　樂則行之，憂則違之；確乎其不可拔，潛龍也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二曰：「見龍在田，利見大人。」何謂也？\n子曰：「龍德而正中者也。庸言之信，庸行之謹，閑邪存其誠，善世而不伐，德博而化。\n易曰：「見龍在田，利見大人。」君德也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三曰：「君子終日乾乾，夕惕，若厲，無咎。」何謂也？<br>\n\n子曰：「君子進德修業，忠信，所以進德也。修辭立其誠，所以居業也。<br>\n\n    知至至之，可與幾也。知終終之，可與存義也。<br>\n\n    是故，居上位而不驕，在下位而不憂。故乾乾因其時而惕，雖危而無咎矣。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：「或躍在淵，無咎。」何謂也？\n子曰：「上下無常，非為邪也。進退無恆，非離群也。君子進德修業，欲及時也，故無咎。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五曰：「飛龍在天，利見大人。」何謂也？\n子曰：「同聲相應，同氣相求；水流濕，火就燥；雲從龍，風從虎。\n　　　　聖人作，而萬物睹，本乎天者親上，本乎地者親下，則各從其類也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九曰：「亢龍有悔。」何謂也？\n子曰：「貴而無位，高而無民，賢人在下而無輔，是以動而有悔也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>潛龍勿用，下也。\n見龍在田，時舍也。終日乾乾，行事也。\n或躍在淵，自試也。\n飛龍在天，上治也。\n亢龍有悔，窮之災也。\n乾元用九，天下治也。\n潛龍勿用，陽氣潛藏。\n見龍在田，天下文明。\n終日乾乾，與時偕行。\n或躍在淵，乾道乃革。\n飛龍在天，乃位乎天德。\n亢龍有悔，與時偕極。\n乾元用九，乃見天則。\n乾元者，始而亨者也。\n利貞者，性情也。\n乾始能以美利利天下，不言所利。\n大矣哉！大哉乾乎？剛健中正，純粹精也。\n六爻發揮，旁通情也。時乘六龍以御天也。雲行雨施，天下平也。\n君子以成德為行，日可見之行也。\n潛之為言也，隱而未見，行未成，是以君子弗用也。\n君子學以聚之，問以辯之，寬以居之，仁以行之。\n易曰：「見龍在田，利見大人。」君德也。\n九三，重剛而不中，上不在天，下不在田。故乾乾因其時而惕，雖危無咎矣。\n九四，重剛而不中，上不在天，下不在田，中不在人，故或之。\n或之者，疑之也，故無咎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>夫大人者，與天地合其德，與日月合其明，與四時合其序，\n與鬼神合其吉凶。先天而天弗違，後天而奉天時。\n天且弗違，而況於人乎？況於鬼神乎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>亢之為言也，知進而不知退，知存而不知亡，知得而不知喪。其唯聖人乎？\n知進退存亡，而不失其正者，其為聖人乎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 二 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">坤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">坤：元，亨，利牝馬之貞。\n　　君子有攸往，先迷後得主，利西南得朋，東北喪朋。安貞，吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：至哉坤元，萬物資生，乃順承天。坤厚載物，德合無疆。含弘光大，品物咸亨。\n　　　牝馬地類，行地無疆，柔順利貞。君子攸行，先迷失道，後順得常。\n　　　西南得朋，乃與類行；東北喪朋，乃終有慶。安貞之吉，應地無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：地勢坤，君子以厚德載物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：履霜，堅冰至。\n象曰：履霜堅冰，陰始凝也。馴致其道，至堅冰也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：直，方，大，不習無不利。\n象曰：六二之動，直以方也。不習無不利，地道光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：含章可貞。或從王事，無成有終。\n象曰：含章可貞；以時發也。或從王事，知光大也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：括囊；無咎，無譽。\n象曰：括囊無咎，慎不害也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：黃裳，元吉。\n象曰：黃裳元吉，文在中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：戰龍於野，其血玄黃。\n象曰：戰龍於野，其道窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>用六：利永貞。\n象曰：用六永貞，以大終也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">文言曰：坤至柔，而動也剛，至靜而德方，後得主而有常，含萬物而化光。\n　　　　坤其道順乎？承天而時行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　　　積善之家，必有餘慶；積不善之家，必有餘殃。\n　　　　臣弒其君，子弒其父，非一朝一夕之故，其所由來者漸矣，由辯之不早辯也。\n　　　　易曰：「履霜堅冰至。」蓋言順也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　　　直其正也，方其義也。君子敬以直內，義以方外，敬義立，而德不孤。\n　　　　「直，方，大，不習無不利」；則不疑其所行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>    陰雖有美，含之；以從王事，弗敢成也。地道也，妻道也，臣道也。<br>\n\n    地道無成，而代有終也。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　　　天地變化，草木蕃；天地閉，賢人隱。\n　　　　易曰：「括囊；無咎，無譽。」蓋言謹也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　　　君子黃中通理，正位居體，美在其中，而暢於四支，發於事業，美之至也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　　　陰疑於陽，必戰。為其嫌於無陽也，故稱龍焉。猶未離其類也，故稱血焉。\n　　　　夫玄黃者，天地之雜也，天玄而地黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 三 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">屯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>屯：元，亨，利，貞，勿用，有攸往，利建侯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：屯，剛柔始交而難生，動乎險中，大亨貞。\n　　　雷雨之動滿盈，天造草昧，宜建侯而不寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雲，雷，屯；君子以經綸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：磐桓；利居貞，利建侯。\n象曰：雖磐桓，志行正也。以貴下賤，大得民也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：屯如邅如，乘馬班如。匪寇婚媾，女子貞不字，十年乃字。\n象曰：六二之難，乘剛也。十年乃字，反常也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：既鹿無虞，惟入于林中，君子幾不如舍，往吝。\n象曰：既鹿無虞，以縱禽也。君子舍之，往吝窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：乘馬班如，求婚媾，往吉，無不利。\n象曰：求而往，明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：屯其膏，小貞吉，大貞凶。\n象曰：屯其膏，施未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：乘馬班如，泣血漣如。\n象曰：泣血漣如，何可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 四 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">蒙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>蒙：亨。匪我求童蒙，童蒙求我。初噬告，再三瀆，瀆則不告。利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：蒙，山下有險，險而止，蒙。蒙，亨，以亨行時中也。\n　　　匪我求童蒙，童蒙求我，志應也。\n　　　初噬告，以剛中也。\n　　　再三瀆，瀆則不告，瀆蒙也。蒙以養正，聖功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山下出泉，蒙；君子以果行育德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：發蒙，利用刑人，用說桎梏，以往吝。\n象曰：利用刑人，以正法也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：包蒙，吉；納婦，吉；子克家。\n象曰：子克家，剛柔接也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：勿用娶女；見金夫，不有躬，無攸利。\n象曰：勿用娶女，行不順也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：困蒙，吝。\n象曰：困蒙之吝，獨遠實也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：童蒙，吉。\n象曰：童蒙之吉，順以巽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：擊蒙；不利為寇，利御寇。\n象曰：利用御寇，上下順也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 五 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">需</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>需：有孚，光亨，貞吉。利涉大川。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：需，須也；險在前也。剛健而不陷，其義不困窮矣。\n　　　需，有孚，光亨，貞吉。位乎天位，以正中也。利涉大川，往有功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雲上於天，需；君子以飲食宴樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：需于郊。利用恆，無咎。\n象曰：需于郊，不犯難行也。利用恆，無咎；未失常也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：需于沙。小有言，終吉。\n象曰：需于沙，衍在中也。雖小有言，以終吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：需于泥，致寇至。\n象曰：需于泥，災在外也。自我致寇，敬慎不敗也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：需于血，出自穴。\n象曰：需于血，順以聽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：需于酒食，貞吉。\n象曰：酒食貞吉，以中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：入于穴，有不速之客三人來，敬之終吉。\n象曰：不速之客來，敬之終吉。雖不當位，未大失也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 六 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">訟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>訟：有孚，窒。惕中吉。終凶。利見大人，不利涉大川。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：訟，上剛下險，險而健，訟。訟有孚窒，惕中吉，剛來而得中也。\n終凶；訟不可成也。利見大人；尚中正也。不利涉大川；入于淵也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天與水違行，訟；君子以作事謀始。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：不永所事，小有言，終吉。\n象曰：不永所事，訟不可長也。雖有小言，其辯明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：不克訟，歸而逋，其邑人三百戶，無眚。\n象曰：不克訟，歸逋竄也。自下訟上，患至掇也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：食舊德，貞厲，終吉，或從王事，無成。\n象曰：食舊德，從上吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：不克訟，復即命，渝安貞，吉。\n象曰：復即命，渝安貞；不失也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：訟元吉。\n象曰：訟元吉，以中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：或錫之鞶帶，終朝三褫之。\n象曰：以訟受服，亦不足敬也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 七 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">師</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>師：貞，丈人，吉無咎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：師，眾也，貞正也，能以眾正，可以王矣。\n　　　剛中而應，行險而順，以此毒天下，而民從之，吉又何咎矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：地中有水，師；君子以容民畜眾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：師出以律，否臧凶。\n象曰：師出以律，失律凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：在師中，吉無咎，王三錫命。\n象曰：在師中吉，承天寵也。王三錫命，懷萬邦也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：師或輿尸，凶。\n象曰：師或輿尸，大無功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：師左次，無咎。\n象曰：左次無咎，未失常也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：田有禽，利執言，無咎。長子帥師，弟子輿尸，貞凶。\n象曰：長子帥師，以中行也。弟子輿師，使不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：大君有命，開國承家，小人勿用。\n象曰：大君有命，以正功也。小人勿用，必亂邦也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 八 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>比：吉。原筮元永貞，無咎。不寧方來，後夫凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：比，吉也，比，輔也，下順從也。原筮元永貞，無咎，以剛中也。\n　　　不寧方來，上下應也。後夫凶，其道窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：地上有水，比；先王以建萬國，親諸侯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：有孚比之，無咎。有孚盈缶，終來有他，吉。\n象曰：比之初六，有他吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：比之自內，貞吉。\n象曰：比之自內，不自失也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：比之匪人。\n象曰：比之匪人，不亦傷乎！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：外比之，貞吉。\n象曰：外比於賢，以從上也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：顯比，王用三驅，失前禽。邑人不誡，吉。\n象曰：顯比之吉，位正中也。舍逆取順，失前禽也。邑人不誡，上使中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：比之無首，凶。\n象曰：比之無首，無所終也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 九 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">小畜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>小畜：亨。密雲不雨，自我西郊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：小畜；柔得位，而上下應之，曰小畜。健而巽，剛中而志行，乃亨。\n　　　密雲不雨，尚往也。自我西郊，施未行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：風行天上，小畜；君子以懿文德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：復自道，何其咎，吉。\n象曰：復自道，其義吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：牽復，吉。\n象曰：牽復在中，亦不自失也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：輿說輻，夫妻反目。\n象曰：夫妻反目，不能正室也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：有孚，血去。惕出，無咎。\n象曰：有孚惕出，上合志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：有孚攣如，富以其鄰。\n象曰：有孚攣如，不獨富也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：既雨既處，尚德載婦，貞厲。月幾望，君子征凶。\n象曰：既雨既處，德積載也。君子征凶，有所疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">履</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>履：履虎尾，不咥人，亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：履，柔履剛也。說而應乎乾，是以履虎尾，不咥人，亨。\n　　　剛中正，履帝位而不疚，光明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：上天下澤，履；君子以辯上下，定民志。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：素履，往無咎。\n象曰：素履之往，獨行願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：履道坦坦，幽人貞吉。\n象曰：幽人貞吉，中不自亂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：眇能視，跛能履，履虎尾，咥人，凶。武人為于大君。\n象曰：眇能視；不足以有明也。跛能履；不足以與行也。咥人之凶；位不當也。\n武人為于大君；志剛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：履虎尾，愬愬，終吉。\n象曰：愬愬終吉，志行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：夬履，貞厲。\n象曰：夬履貞厲，位正當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：視履考祥，其旋元吉。\n象曰：元吉在上，大有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十一 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">泰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>泰：小往大來，吉亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：泰，小往大來，吉亨。則是天地交，而萬物通也；上下交，而其志同也。\n　　　內陽而外陰，內健而外順，內君子而外小人，君子道長，小人道消也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天地交泰，后以財成天地之道，輔相天地之宜，以左右民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：拔茅茹，以其彙，征吉。\n象曰：拔茅征吉，志在外也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：包荒，用馮河，不遐遺，朋亡，得尚于中行。\n象曰：包荒，得尚于中行，以光大也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：無平不陂，無往不復，艱貞無咎。勿恤其孚，于食有福。\n象曰：無往不復，天地際也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：翩翩不富，以其鄰，不戒以孚。\n象曰：翩翩不富，皆失實也。不戒以孚，中心願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：帝乙歸妹，以祉元吉。\n象曰：以祉元吉，中以行願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：城復于隍，勿用師。自邑告命，貞吝。\n象曰：城復于隍，其命亂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十二 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">否</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>否：否之匪人，不利君子貞，大往小來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：否之匪人，不利君子貞。大往小來，則是天地不交，而萬物不通也；\n　　　上下不交，而天下無邦也。內陰而外陽，內柔而外剛，內小人而外君子。\n　　　小人道長，君子道消也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天地不交，否；君子以儉德辟難，不可榮以祿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：拔茅茹，以其彙，貞吉亨。\n象曰：拔茅貞吉，志在君也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：包承。小人吉，大人否亨。\n象曰：大人否亨，不亂群也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：包羞。\n象曰：包羞，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：有命無咎，疇離祉。\n象曰：有命無咎，志行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：休否，大人吉。其亡其亡，繫于苞桑。\n象曰：大人之吉，位正當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：傾否，先否後喜。\n象曰：否終則傾，何可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十三 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">同人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>同人：同人于野，亨。利涉大川，利君子貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：同人，柔得位得中，而應乎乾，曰同人。同人曰：同人于野，亨。\n　　　利涉大川，乾行也。文明以健，中正而應，君子正也。唯君子為能通天下之志。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天與火，同人；君子以類族辨物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：同人于門，無咎。\n象曰：出門同人，又誰咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：同人于宗，吝。\n象曰：同人于宗，吝道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：伏戎于莽，升其高陵，三歲不興。\n象曰：伏戎于莽，敵剛也。三歲不興，安行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：乘其墉，弗克攻，吉。\n象曰：乘其墉，義弗克也，其吉，則困而反則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：同人，先號咷而後笑。大師克相遇。\n象曰：同人之先，以中直也。大師相遇，言相克也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：同人于郊，無悔。\n象曰：同人于郊，志未得也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十四 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>大有：元亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：大有，柔得尊位，大中而上下應之，曰大有。\n　　　其德剛健而文明，應乎天而時行，是以元亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：火在天上，大有；君子以遏惡揚善，順天休命。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：無交害，匪咎，艱則無咎。\n象曰：大有初九，無交害也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：大車以載，有攸往，無咎。\n象曰：大車以載，積中不敗也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：公用亨于天子，小人弗克。\n象曰：公用亨于天子，小人害也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：匪其彭，無咎。\n象曰：匪其彭，無咎；明辨晢也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：厥孚交如，威如；吉。\n象曰：厥孚交如，信以發志也。威如之吉，易而無備也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：自天佑之，吉無不利。\n象曰：大有上吉，自天佑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十五 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">謙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>謙：亨，君子有終。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：謙，亨，天道下濟而光明，地道卑而上行。天道虧盈而益謙，地道變盈而流謙，\n　　　鬼神害盈而福謙，人道惡盈而好謙。謙尊而光，卑而不可踰，君子之終也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：地中有山，謙；君子以裒多益寡，稱物平施。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：謙謙君子，用涉大川，吉。\n象曰：謙謙君子，卑以自牧也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：鳴謙，貞吉。\n象曰：鳴謙貞吉，中心得也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：勞謙君子，有終吉。\n象曰：勞謙君子，萬民服也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：無不利，撝謙。\n象曰：無不利，撝謙；不違則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：不富，以其鄰，利用侵伐，無不利。\n象曰：利用侵伐，征不服也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：鳴謙，利用行師，征邑國。\n象曰：鳴謙，志未得也。可用行師，征邑國也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十六 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">豫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>豫：利建侯行師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：豫，剛應而志行，順以動，豫。豫，順以動，故天地如之，而況建侯行師乎？\n　　　天地以順動，故日月不過，而四時不忒；\n　　　聖人以順動，則刑罰清而民服。豫之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷出地奮，豫。先王以作樂崇德，殷薦之上帝，以配祖考。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：鳴豫，凶。\n象曰：初六鳴豫，志窮凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：介于石，不終日，貞吉。\n象曰：不終日，貞吉；以中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：盱豫，悔。遲有悔。\n象曰：盱豫有悔，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：由豫，大有得。勿疑。朋盍簪。\n象曰：由豫，大有得；志大行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：貞疾，恆不死。\n象曰：六五貞疾，乘剛也。恆不死，中未亡也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：冥豫，成有渝，無咎。\n象曰：冥豫在上，何可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十七 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">隨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>隨：元亨利貞，無咎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：隨，剛來而下柔，動而說，隨。大亨貞，無咎，而天下隨時，隨之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤中有雷，隨；君子以嚮晦入宴息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：官有渝，貞吉。出門交有功。\n象曰：官有渝，從正吉也。出門交有功，不失也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：係小子，失丈夫。\n象曰：係小子，弗兼與也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：係丈夫，失小子。隨有求得，利居貞。\n象曰：係丈夫，志舍下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：隨有獲，貞凶。有孚在道，以明，何咎。\n象曰：隨有獲，其義凶也。有孚在道，明功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：孚于嘉，吉。\n象曰：孚于嘉，吉；位正中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：拘系之，乃從維之。王用亨于西山。\n象曰：拘系之，上窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十八 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">蠱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>蠱：元亨，利涉大川。先甲三日，後甲三日。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：蠱，剛上而柔下，巽而止，蠱。蠱，元亨，而天下治也。利涉大川，往有事也。\n　　　先甲三日，後甲三日，終則有始，天行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山下有風，蠱；君子以振民育德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：幹父之蠱，有子，考無咎，厲終吉。\n象曰：幹父之蠱，意承考也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：幹母之蠱，不可貞。\n象曰：幹母之蠱，得中道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：幹父小有晦，無大咎。\n象曰：幹父之蠱，終無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：裕父之蠱，往見吝。\n象曰：裕父之蠱，往未得也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：幹父之蠱，用譽。\n象曰：幹父之蠱；承以德也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：不事王侯，高尚其事。\n象曰：不事王侯，志可則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 十九 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">臨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>臨：元，亨，利，貞。至于八月有凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：臨，剛浸而長。說而順，剛中而應，大亨以正，天之道也。至于八月有凶，消不久也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上有地，臨；君子以教思無窮，容保民無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：咸臨，貞吉。\n象曰：咸臨貞吉，志行正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：咸臨，吉無不利。\n象曰：咸臨，吉無不利；未順命也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：甘臨，無攸利。既憂之，無咎。\n象曰：甘臨，位不當也。既憂之，咎不長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：至臨，無咎。\n象曰：至臨無咎，位當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：知臨，大君之宜，吉。\n象曰：大君之宜，行中之謂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：敦臨，吉無咎。\n象曰：敦臨之吉，志在內也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 二十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>觀：盥而不薦，有孚顒若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：大觀在上，順而巽，中正以觀天下。觀，盥而不薦，有孚顒若，下觀而化也。\n觀天之神道，而四時不忒，聖人以神道設教，而天下服矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：風行地上，觀；先王以省方，觀民設教。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：童觀，小人無咎，君子吝。\n象曰：初六童觀，小人道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：窺觀，利女貞。\n象曰：窺觀女貞，亦可醜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：觀我生，進退。\n象曰：觀我生，進退；未失道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：觀國之光，利用賓于王。\n象曰：觀國之光，尚賓也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：觀我生，君子無咎。\n象曰：觀我生，觀民也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：觀其生，君子無咎。\n象曰：觀其生，志未平也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十一卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">噬嗑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>噬嗑：亨。利用獄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：頤中有物，曰噬嗑，噬嗑而亨。剛柔分，動而明，雷電合而章。\n　　　柔得中而上行，雖不當位，利用獄也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷電噬嗑；先王以明罰敕法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：履校滅趾，無咎。\n象曰：履校滅趾，不行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：噬膚滅鼻，無咎。\n象曰：噬膚滅鼻，乘剛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：噬臘肉，遇毒；小吝，無咎。\n象曰：遇毒，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：噬乾胏，得金矢，利艱貞，吉。\n象曰：利艱貞吉，未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：噬乾肉，得黃金，貞厲，無咎。\n象曰：貞厲無咎，得當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：何校滅耳，凶。\n象曰：何校滅耳，聰不明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十二卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">賁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>賁：亨。小利有所往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：賁，亨；柔來而文剛，故亨。分剛上而文柔，故小利有攸往。\n　　　天文也；文明以止，人文也。觀乎天文，以察時變；觀乎人文，以化成天下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山下有火，賁；君子以明庶政，無敢折獄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：賁其趾，舍車而徒。\n象曰：舍車而徒，義弗乘也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：賁其須。\n象曰：賁其須，與上興也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：賁如濡如，永貞吉。\n象曰：永貞之吉，終莫之陵也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：賁如皤如，白馬翰如，匪寇婚媾。\n象曰：六四，當位疑也。匪寇婚媾，終無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：賁于丘園，束帛戔戔，吝，終吉。\n象曰：六五之吉，有喜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：白賁，無咎。\n象曰：白賁無咎，上得志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十三卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">剝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>剝：不利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：剝，剝也，柔變剛也。不利有攸往，小人長也。順而止之，觀象也。\n　　　君子尚消息盈虛，天行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山附于地，剝；上以厚下，安宅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：剝床以足，蔑貞凶。\n象曰：剝床以足，以滅下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：剝床以辨，蔑貞凶。\n象曰：剝床以辨，未有與也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：剝之，無咎。\n象曰：剝之無咎，失上下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：剝床以膚，凶。\n象曰：剝床以膚，切近災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：貫魚，以宮人寵，無不利。\n象曰：以宮人寵，終無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：碩果不食，君子得輿，小人剝廬。\n象曰：君子得輿，民所載也。小人剝廬，終不可用也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十四卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">復</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>復：亨。出入無疾，朋來無咎。反復其道，七日來復，利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：復亨；剛反，動而以順行，是以出入無疾，朋來無咎。反復其道，\n　　　七日來復，天行也。利有攸往，剛長也。復其見天地之心乎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷在地中，復；先王以至日閉關，商旅不行，后不省方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：不復遠，無祗悔，元吉。\n象曰：不遠之復，以修身也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：休復，吉。\n象曰：休復之吉，以下仁也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：頻復厲，無咎。\n象曰：頻復之厲，義無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：中行獨復。\n象曰：中行獨復，以從道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：敦復，無悔。\n象曰：敦復無悔，中以自考也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：迷復，凶，有災眚。用行師，終有大敗，以其國君，凶；至于十年，不克征。\n象曰：迷復之凶，反君道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十五卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">無妄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>無妄：元，亨，利，貞。其匪正有眚，不利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：無妄，剛自外來，而為主於內。動而健，剛中而應，大亨以正，天之命也。\n　　　其匪正有眚，不利有攸往。無妄之往，何之矣？天命不佑，行矣哉？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天下雷行，物與無妄；先王以茂對時，育萬物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：無妄，往吉。\n象曰：無妄之往，得志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：不耕獲，不菑畬，則利有攸往。\n象曰：不耕獲，未富也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：無妄之災，或繫之牛，行人之得，邑人之災。\n象曰：行人得牛，邑人災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：可貞，無咎。\n象曰：可貞無咎，固有之也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：無妄之疾，勿藥有喜。\n象曰：無妄之藥，不可試也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：無妄，行有眚，無攸利。\n象曰：無妄之行，窮之災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十六卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大畜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>大畜：利貞，不家食吉，利涉大川。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：大畜，剛健，篤實輝光，日新其德，剛上而尚賢。能止健，大正也。\n　　　不家食吉，養賢也。利涉大川，應乎天也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天在山中，大畜；君子以多識前言往行，以畜其德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：有厲利已。\n象曰：有厲利已，不犯災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：輿說輻。\n象曰：輿說輻，中無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：良馬逐，利艱貞。日閑輿衛，利有攸往。\n象曰：利有攸往，上合志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：童牛之牿，元吉。\n象曰：六四元吉，有喜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：豶豕之牙，吉。\n象曰：六五之吉，有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：何天之衢，亨。\n象曰：何天之衢，道大行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十七卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">頤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>頤：貞吉。觀頤，自求口實。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：頤，貞吉，養正則吉。觀頤，觀其所養也；自求口實，觀其自養也。\n　　　天地養萬物，聖人養賢以及萬民；頤之時大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山下有雷，頤；君子以慎言語，節飲食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：舍爾靈龜，觀我朵頤，凶。\n象曰：觀我朵頤，亦不足貴也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：顛頤，拂經于丘頤，征凶。\n象曰：六二征凶，行失類也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：拂頤，貞凶，十年勿用，無攸利。\n象曰：十年勿用，道大悖也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：顛頤吉，虎視眈眈，其欲逐逐，無咎。\n象曰：顛頤之吉，上施光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：拂經，居貞吉，不可涉大川。\n象曰：居貞之吉，順以從上也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：由頤，厲吉，利涉大川。\n象曰：由頤厲吉，大有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十八卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>大過：棟橈，利有攸往，亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：大過，大者過也。棟橈，本末弱也。剛過而中，巽而說行，利有攸往，乃亨。\n　　　大過之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤滅木，大過；君子以獨立不懼，遯世無悶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：藉用白茅，無咎。\n象曰：藉用白茅，柔在下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：枯楊生稊，老夫得其女妻，無不利。\n象曰：老夫女妻，過以相與也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：棟橈，凶。\n象曰：棟橈之凶，不可以有輔也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：棟隆，吉；有它吝。\n象曰：棟隆之吉，不橈乎下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：枯楊生華，老婦得士夫，無咎無譽。\n象曰：枯楊生華，何可久也。老婦士夫，亦可醜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：過涉滅頂，凶，無咎。\n象曰：過涉之凶，不可咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二十九卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">坎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>坎：習坎，有孚，維心亨，行有尚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：習坎，重險也。水流而不盈，行險而不失其信。維心亨，乃以剛中也。\n　　　行有尚，往有功也。天險不可升也，地險山川丘陵也，\n　　　王公設險以守其國，坎之時用大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：水洊至，習坎；君子以常德行，習教事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：習坎，入于坎窞，凶。\n象曰：習坎入坎，失道凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：坎有險，求小得。\n象曰：求小得，未出中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：來之坎坎，險且枕，入于坎窞，勿用。\n象曰：來之坎坎，終無功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：樽酒簋貳，用缶，納約自牖，終無咎。\n象曰：樽酒簋貳，剛柔際也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：坎不盈，祗既平，無咎。\n象曰：坎不盈，中未大也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：係用徽纆，寘于叢棘，三歲不得，凶。\n象曰：上六失道，凶三歲也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 三十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">離</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>離：利貞，亨。畜牝牛，吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：離，麗也；日月麗乎天，百穀草木麗乎土，重明以麗乎正，乃化成天下。\n　　　柔麗乎中正，故亨；是以畜牝牛吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：明兩作離，大人以繼明照于四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：履錯然，敬之無咎。\n象曰：履錯之敬，以辟咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：黃離，元吉。\n象曰：黃離元吉，得中道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：日昃之離，不鼓缶而歌，則大耋之嗟，凶。\n象曰：日昃之離，何可久也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：突如其來如，焚如，死如，棄如。\n象曰：突如其來如，無所容也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：出涕沱若，戚嗟若，吉。\n象曰：六五之吉，離王公也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：王用出征，有嘉折首，獲匪其醜，無咎。\n象曰：王用出征，以正邦也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十一卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">咸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>咸：亨，利貞，取女吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：咸，感也。柔上而剛下，二氣感應以相與，止而說，男下女，是以亨利貞，取女吉也。\n　　　天地感而萬物化生，聖人感人心而天下和平；觀其所感，而天地萬物之情可見矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山上有澤，咸；君子以虛受人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：咸其拇。\n象曰：咸其拇，志在外也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：咸其腓，凶，居吉。\n象曰：雖凶，居吉，順不害也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：咸其股，執其隨，往吝。\n象曰：咸其股，亦不處也。志在隨人，所執下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：貞吉悔亡，憧憧往來，朋從爾思。\n象曰：貞吉悔亡，未感害也。憧憧往來，未光大也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：咸其脢，無悔。\n象曰：咸其脢，志末也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：咸其輔，頰，舌。\n象曰：咸其輔，頰，舌，滕口說也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十二卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">恆：亨，無咎，利貞，利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：恆，久也。剛上而柔下，雷風相與，巽而動，剛柔皆應，恆。\n　　　恆亨無咎，利貞；久於其道也，天地之道，恆久而不已也。\n　　　利有攸往，終則有始也。日月得天，而能久照，四時變化，而能久成，\n　　　聖人久於其道，而天下化成；觀其所恆，而天地萬物之情可見矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷風，恆；君子以立不易方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：浚恆，貞凶，無攸利。\n象曰：浚恆之凶，始求深也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：悔亡。\n象曰：九二悔亡，能久中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：不恆其德，或承之羞，貞吝。\n象曰：不恆其德，無所容也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：田無禽。\n象曰：久非其位，安得禽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：恆其德，貞，婦人吉，夫子凶。\n象曰：婦人貞吉，從一而終也。夫子制義，從婦凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：振恆，凶。\n象曰：振恆在上，大無功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十三卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">遯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>遯：亨，小利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：遯亨，遯而亨也。剛當位而應，與時行也。小利貞，浸而長也。\n　　　遯之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天下有山，遯；君子以遠小人，不惡而嚴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：遯尾，厲，勿用有攸往。\n象曰：遯尾之厲，不往何災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：執之用黃牛之革，莫之勝說。\n象曰：執用黃牛，固志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：係遯，有疾厲，畜臣妾吉。\n象曰：係遯之厲，有疾憊也。畜臣妾吉，不可大事也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：好遯君子吉，小人否。\n象曰：君子好遯，小人否也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：嘉遯，貞吉。\n象曰：嘉遯貞吉，以正志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：肥遯，無不利。\n象曰：肥遯，無不利；無所疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十四卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大壯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>大壯：利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：大壯，大者壯也。剛以動，故壯。大壯利貞；大者正也。正大而天地之情可見矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷在天上，大壯；君子以非禮弗履。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：壯于趾，征凶，有孚。\n象曰：壯于趾，其孚窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：貞吉。\n象曰：九二貞吉，以中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：小人用壯，君子用罔，貞厲。羝羊觸藩，羸其角。\n象曰：小人用壯，君子罔也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：貞吉悔亡，藩決不羸，壯于大輿之輹。\n象曰：藩決不羸，尚往也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：喪羊于易，無悔。\n象曰：喪羊于易，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：羝羊觸藩，不能退，不能遂，無攸利，艱則吉。\n象曰：不能退，不能遂，不祥也。艱則吉，咎不長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十五卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">晉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>晉：康侯用錫馬蕃庶，晝日三接。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：晉，進也。明出地上，順而麗乎大明，柔進而上行。是以康侯用錫馬蕃庶，晝日三接也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：明出地上，晉；君子以自昭明德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：晉如，摧如，貞吉。罔孚，裕無咎。\n象曰：晉如，摧如；獨行正也。裕無咎；未受命也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：晉如，愁如，貞吉。受茲介福，于其王母。\n象曰：受茲介福，以中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：眾允，悔亡。\n象曰：眾允之，志上行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：晉如鼫鼠，貞厲。\n象曰：鼫鼠貞厲，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：悔亡，失得勿恤，往吉無不利。\n象曰：失得勿恤，往有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：晉其角，維用伐邑，厲吉無咎，貞吝。\n象曰：維用伐邑，道未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十六卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">明夷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>明夷：利艱貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：明入地中，明夷。內文明而外柔順，以蒙大難，文王以之。利艱貞，\n　　　晦其明也，內難而能正其志，箕子以之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：明入地中，明夷；君子以蒞眾，用晦而明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：明夷于飛，垂其翼。君子于行，三日不食，有攸往，主人有言。\n象曰：君子于行，義不食也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：明夷，夷于左股，用拯馬壯，吉。\n象曰：六二之吉，順以則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：明夷于南狩，得其大首，不可疾貞。\n象曰：南狩之志，乃大得也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：入于左腹，獲明夷之心，于出門庭。\n象曰：入于左腹，獲心意也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：箕子之明夷，利貞。\n象曰：箕子之貞，明不可息也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：不明晦，初登于天，後入于地。\n象曰：初登于天，照四國也。後入于地，失則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十七卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>家人：利女貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：家人，女正位乎內，男正位乎外，男女正，天地之大義也。\n　　　家人有嚴君焉，父母之謂也。\n　　　父父，子子，兄兄，弟弟，夫夫，婦婦，而家道正；正家而天下定矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：風自火出，家人；君子以言有物，而行有恆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：閑有家，悔亡。\n象曰：閑有家，志未變也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：無攸遂，在中饋，貞吉。\n象曰：六二之吉，順以巽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：家人嗃嗃，悔厲吉；婦子嘻嘻，終吝。\n象曰：家人嗃嗃，未失也；婦子嘻嘻，失家節也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：富家，大吉。\n象曰：富家大吉，順在位也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：王假有家，勿恤吉。\n象曰：王假有家，交相愛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：有孚威如，終吉。\n象曰：威如之吉，反身之謂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十八卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">睽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>睽：小事吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：睽，火動而上，澤動而下；二女同居，其志不同行；\n　　　說而麗乎明，柔進而上行，得中而應乎剛；是以小事吉。\n　　　天地睽，而其事同也；男女睽，而其志通也；\n　　　萬物睽，而其事類也；睽之時用大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：上火下澤，睽；君子以同而異。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：悔亡，喪馬勿逐，自復；見惡人無咎。\n象曰：見惡人，以辟咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：遇主于巷，無咎。\n象曰：遇主于巷，未失道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：見輿曳，其牛掣，其人天且劓，無初有終。\n象曰：見輿曳，位不當也。無初有終，遇剛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：睽孤，遇元夫，交孚，厲無咎。\n象曰：交孚無咎，志行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：悔亡，厥宗噬膚，往何咎。\n象曰：厥宗噬膚，往有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：睽孤，見豕負塗，載鬼一車，先張之弧，後說之弧，匪寇婚媾，往遇雨則吉。\n象曰：遇雨之吉，群疑亡也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第三十九卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">蹇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>蹇：利西南，不利東北；利見大人，貞吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：蹇，難也，險在前也。見險而能止，知矣哉！蹇利西南，往得中也；\n　　　不利東北，其道窮也。利見大人，往有功也。當位貞吉，以正邦也。蹇之時用大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山上有水，蹇；君子以反身修德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：往蹇，來譽。\n象曰：往蹇來譽，宜待也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：王臣蹇蹇，匪躬之故。\n象曰：王臣蹇蹇，終無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：往蹇來反。\n象曰：往蹇來反，內喜之也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：往蹇來連。\n象曰：往蹇來連，當位實也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：大蹇朋來。\n象曰：大蹇朋來，以中節也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：往蹇來碩，吉；利見大人。\n象曰：往蹇來碩，志在內也。利見大人，以從貴也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 四十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">解</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>解：利西南，無所往，其來復吉。有攸往，夙吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：解，險以動，動而免乎險，解。解利西南，往得眾也。其來復吉，乃得中也。\n　　　有攸往夙吉，往有功也。天地解，而雷雨作，雷雨作，而百果草木皆甲坼，\n　　　解之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷雨作，解；君子以赦過宥罪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：無咎。\n象曰：剛柔之際，義無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：田獲三狐，得黃矢，貞吉。\n象曰：九二貞吉，得中道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：負且乘，致寇至，貞吝。\n象曰：負且乘，亦可醜也，自我致戎，又誰咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：解而拇，朋至斯孚。\n象曰：解而拇，未當位也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：君子維有解，吉；有孚于小人。\n象曰：君子有解，小人退也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：公用射隼，于高墉之上，獲之，無不利。\n象曰：公用射隼，以解悖也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十一卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">損</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>損：有孚，元吉，無咎，可貞，利有攸往？曷之用，二簋可用享。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：損，損下益上，其道上行。損而有孚，元吉，無咎，可貞，利有攸往。\n　　　曷之用？二簋可用享；二簋應有時。損剛益柔有時，損益盈虛，與時偕行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山下有澤，損；君子以懲忿窒欲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：已事遄往，無咎，酌損之。\n象曰：已事遄往，尚合志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：利貞，征凶，弗損益之。\n象曰：九二利貞，中以為志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：三人行，則損一人；一人行，則得其友。\n象曰：一人行，三則疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：損其疾，使遄有喜，無咎。\n象曰：損其疾，亦可喜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：或益之，十朋之龜弗克違，元吉。\n象曰：六五元吉，自上祐也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：弗損益之，無咎，貞吉，利有攸往，得臣無家。\n象曰：弗損益之，大得志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十二卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">益</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>益：利有攸往，利涉大川。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：益，損上益下，民說無疆，自上下下，其道大光。\n　　　利有攸往，中正有慶。利涉大川，木道乃行。\n　　　益動而巽，日進無疆。天施地生，\n　　　其益無方。凡益之道，與時偕行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：風雷，益；君子以見善則遷，有過則改。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：利用為大作，元吉，無咎。\n象曰：元吉無咎，下不厚事也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：或益之，十朋之龜弗克違，永貞吉。王用享于帝，吉。\n象曰：或益之，自外來也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：益之用凶事，無咎。有孚中行，告公用圭。\n象曰：益用凶事，固有之也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：中行，告公從。利用為依遷國。\n象曰：告公從，以益志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：有孚惠心，勿問元吉。有孚惠我德。\n象曰：有孚惠心，勿問之矣。惠我德，大得志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：莫益之，或擊之，立心勿恆，凶。\n象曰：莫益之，偏辭也。或擊之，自外來也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十三卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">夬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>夬：揚于王庭，孚號，有厲，告自邑，不利即戎，利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：夬，決也，剛決柔也。健而說，決而和，揚于王庭，柔乘五剛也。\n　　　孚號有厲，其危乃光也。告自邑，不利即戎，所尚乃窮也。\n　　　利有攸往，剛長乃終也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上于天，夬；君子以施祿及下，居德則忌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：壯于前趾，往不勝為吝。\n象曰：不勝而往，咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：惕號，莫夜有戎，勿恤。\n象曰：有戎勿恤，得中道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：壯于頄，有凶。君子夬夬，獨行遇雨，若濡有慍，無咎。\n象曰：君子夬夬，終無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：臀無膚，其行次且。牽羊悔亡，聞言不信。\n象曰：其行次且，位不當也。聞言不信，聰不明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：莧陸夬夬，中行無咎。\n象曰：中行無咎，中未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：無號，終有凶。\n象曰：無號之凶，終不可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十四卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">姤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>姤：女壯，勿用取女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：姤，遇也，柔遇剛也。勿用取女，不可與長也。天地相遇，品物咸章也。\n　　　剛遇中正，天下大行也。姤之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：天下有風，姤；后以施命誥四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：繫于金柅，貞吉，有攸往，見凶，羸豕孚蹢躅。\n象曰：繫于金柅，柔道牽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：包有魚，無咎，不利賓。\n象曰：包有魚，義不及賓也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：臀無膚，其行次且，厲，無大咎。\n象曰：其行次且，行未牽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：包無魚，起凶。\n象曰：無魚之凶，遠民也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：以杞包瓜，含章，有隕自天。\n象曰：九五含章，中正也。有隕自天，志不舍命也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：姤其角，吝，無咎。\n象曰：姤其角，上窮吝也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十五卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">萃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>萃：亨。王假有廟，利見大人，亨，利貞。用大牲吉，利有攸往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：萃，聚也；順以說，剛中而應，故聚也。王假有廟，致孝享也。\n　　　利見大人亨，聚以正也。用大牲吉，利有攸往，順天命也。\n　　　觀其所聚，而天地萬物之情可見矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上於地，萃；君子以除戎器，戒不虞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：有孚不終，乃亂乃萃，若號一握為笑，勿恤，往無咎。\n象曰：乃亂乃萃，其志亂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：引吉，無咎，孚乃利用禴。\n象曰：引吉無咎，中未變也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：萃如，嗟如，無攸利，往無咎，小吝。\n象曰：往無咎，上巽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：大吉，無咎。\n象曰：大吉無咎，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：萃有位，無咎。匪孚，元永貞，悔亡。\n象曰：萃有位，志未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：齎咨涕洟，無咎。\n象曰：齎咨涕洟，未安上也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十六卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">升</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>升：元亨，用見大人，勿恤，南征吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：柔以時升，巽而順，剛中而應，是以大亨。用見大人，勿恤；有慶也。\n　　　南征吉，志行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：地中生木，升；君子以順德，積小以高大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：允升，大吉。\n象曰：允升大吉，上合志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：孚乃利用禴，無咎。\n象曰：九二之孚，有喜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：升虛邑。\n象曰：升虛邑，無所疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：王用亨于岐山，吉無咎。\n象曰：王用亨于岐山，順事也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：貞吉，升階。\n象曰：貞吉升階，大得志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：冥升，利于不息之貞。\n象曰：冥升在上，消不富也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十七卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">困</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>困：亨，貞，大人吉，無咎，有言不信。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：困，剛揜也。險以說，困而不失其所，亨；其唯君子乎？\n　　　貞大人吉，以剛中也。有言不信，尚口乃窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤無水，困；君子以致命遂志。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：臀困于株木，入于幽谷，三歲不覿。\n象曰：入于幽谷，幽不明也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：困于酒食，朱紱方來，利用亨祀，征凶，無咎。\n象曰：困于酒食，中有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：困于石，據于蒺藜，入于其宮，不見其妻，凶。\n象曰：據于蒺藜，乘剛也。入于其宮，不見其妻，不祥也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：來徐徐，困于金車，吝，有終。\n象曰：來徐徐，志在下也。雖不當位，有與也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：劓刖，困于赤紱，乃徐有說，利用祭祀。\n象曰：劓刖，志未得也。乃徐有說，以中直也。利用祭祀，受福也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：困于葛藟，于臲卼，曰動悔。有悔，征吉。\n象曰：困于葛藟，未當也。動悔，有悔吉，行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十八卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">井</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>井：改邑不改井，無喪無得，往來井井。汔至，亦未繘井，羸其瓶，凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：巽乎水而上水，井；井養而不窮也。改邑不改井，乃以剛中也。\n　　　汔至亦未繘井，未有功也。羸其瓶，是以凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：木上有水，井；君子以勞民勸相。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：井泥不食，舊井無禽。\n象曰：井泥不食，下也。舊井無禽，時舍也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：井谷射鮒，甕敝漏。\n象曰：井谷射鮒，無與也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：井渫不食，為我民惻，可用汲，王明，並受其福。\n象曰：井渫不食，行惻也。求王明，受福也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：井甃，無咎。\n象曰：井甃無咎，修井也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：井冽，寒泉食。\n象曰：寒泉之食，中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：井收勿幕，有孚無吉。\n象曰：元吉在上，大成也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第四十九卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">革</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>革：己日乃孚，元亨利貞，悔亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：革，水火相息，二女同居，其志不相得，曰革。己日乃孚；革而信也。\n　　　文明以說，大亨以正，革而當，其悔乃亡。\n　　　天地革而四時成，湯武革命，順乎天而應乎人，革之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤中有火，革；君子以治歷明時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：鞏用黃牛之革。\n象曰：鞏用黃牛，不可以有為也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：己日乃革之，征吉，無咎。\n象曰：己日革之，行有嘉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：征凶，貞厲，革言三就，有孚。\n象曰：革言三就，又何之矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：悔亡，有孚改命，吉。\n象曰：改命之吉，信志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：大人虎變，未占有孚。\n象曰：大人虎變，其文炳也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：君子豹變，小人革面，征凶，居貞吉。\n象曰：君子豹變，其文蔚也。小人革面，順以從君也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 五十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">鼎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>鼎：元吉，亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：鼎，象也。以木巽火，亨飪也。聖人亨以享上帝，而大亨以養聖賢。\n　　　巽而耳目聰明，柔進而上行，得中而應乎剛，是以元亨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：木上有火，鼎；君子以正位凝命。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：鼎顛趾，利出否，得妾以其子，無咎。\n象曰：鼎顛趾，未悖也。利出否，以從貴也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：鼎有實，我仇有疾，不我能即，吉。\n象曰：鼎有實，慎所之也。我仇有疾，終無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：鼎耳革，其行塞，雉膏不食，方雨虧悔，終吉。\n象曰：鼎耳革，失其義也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：鼎折足，覆公餗，其形渥，凶。\n象曰：覆公餗，信如何也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：鼎黃耳金鉉，利貞。\n象曰：鼎黃耳，中以為實也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：鼎玉鉉，大吉，無不利。\n象曰：玉鉉在上，剛柔節也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十一卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">震</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>震：亨。震來虩虩，笑言啞啞。震驚百里，不喪匕鬯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：震，亨。震來虩虩，恐致福也。笑言啞啞，後有則也。\n　　　震驚百里，驚遠而懼邇也。出可以守宗廟社稷，以為祭主也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：洊雷，震；君子以恐懼修身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：震來虩虩，後笑言啞啞，吉。\n象曰：震來虩虩，恐致福也。笑言啞啞，後有則也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：震來厲，億喪貝，躋于九陵，勿逐，七日得。\n象曰：震來厲，乘剛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：震蘇蘇，震行無眚。\n象曰：震蘇蘇，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：震遂泥。\n象曰：震遂泥，未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：震往來厲，億無喪，有事。\n象曰：震往來厲，危行也。其事在中，大無喪也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：震索索，視矍矍，征凶。震不于其躬，于其鄰，無咎。婚媾有言。\n象曰：震索索，未得中也。雖凶無咎，畏鄰戒也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十二卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">艮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>艮：艮其背，不獲其身，行其庭，不見其人，無咎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：艮，止也。時止則止，時行則行，動靜不失其時，其道光明。\n　　　艮其止，止其所也。上下敵應，不相與也。是以不獲其身，行其庭不見其人，無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：兼山，艮；君子以思不出其位。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：艮其趾，無咎，利永貞。\n象曰：艮其趾，未失正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：艮其腓，不拯其隨，其心不快。\n象曰：不拯其隨，未退聽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：艮其限，列其夤，厲薰心。\n象曰：艮其限，危薰心也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：艮其身，無咎。\n象曰：艮其身，止諸躬也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：艮其輔，言有序，悔亡。\n象曰：艮其輔，以中正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：敦艮，吉。\n象曰：敦艮之吉，以厚終也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十三卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">漸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>漸：女歸吉，利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：漸之進也，女歸吉也。進得位，往有功也。進以正，可以正邦也。\n　　　其位剛，得中也。止而巽，動不窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山上有木，漸；君子以居賢德，善俗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：鴻漸于干，小子厲，有言，無咎。\n象曰：小子之厲，義無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：鴻漸于磐，飲食衎衎，吉。\n象曰：飲食衎衎，不素飽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：鴻漸于陸，夫征不復，婦孕不育，凶；利御寇。\n象曰：夫征不復，離群醜也。婦孕不育，失其道也。利用御寇，順相保也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：鴻漸于木，或得其桷，無咎。\n象曰：或得其桷，順以巽也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：鴻漸于陵，婦三歲不孕，終莫之勝，吉。\n象曰：終莫之勝，吉；得所願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：鴻漸于逵，其羽可用為儀，吉。\n象曰：其羽可用為儀，吉；不可亂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十四卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">歸妹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>歸妹：征凶，無攸利。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：歸妹，天地之大義也。天地不交，而萬物不興，歸妹人之終始也。\n　　　說以動，所歸妹也。征凶，位不當也。無攸利，柔乘剛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上有雷，歸妹；君子以永終知敝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：歸妹以娣，跛能履，征吉。\n象曰：歸妹以娣，以恆也。跛能履吉，相承也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：眇能視，利幽人之貞。\n象曰：利幽人之貞，未變常也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：歸妹以須，反歸以娣。\n象曰：歸妹以須，未當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：歸妹愆期，遲歸有時。\n象曰：愆期之志，有待而行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：帝乙歸妹，其君之袂，不如其娣之袂良，月幾望，吉。\n象曰：帝乙歸妹，不如其娣之袂良也。其位在中，以貴行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：女承筐無實，士刲羊無血，無攸利。\n象曰：上六無實，承虛筐也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十五卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">豐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>豐：亨，王假之，勿憂，宜日中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：豐，大也。明以動，故豐。王假之，尚大也。勿憂宜日中，宜照天下也。\n　　　日中則昃，月盈則食，天地盈虛，與時消息，而況於人乎？況於鬼神乎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：雷電皆至，豐；君子以折獄致刑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：遇其配主，雖旬無咎，往有尚。\n象曰：雖旬無咎，過旬災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：豐其蔀，日中見斗，往得疑疾，有孚發若，吉。\n象曰：有孚發若，信以發志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：豐其沛，日中見沫，折其右肱，無咎。\n象曰：豐其沛，不可大事也。折其右肱，終不可用也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：豐其蔀，日中見斗，遇其夷主，吉。\n象曰：豐其蔀，位不當也。日中見斗，幽不明也。遇其夷主，吉；行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：來章，有慶譽，吉。\n象曰：六五之吉，有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：豐其屋，蔀其家，窺其戶，闃其無人，三歲不覿，凶。\n象曰：豐其屋，天際翔也。窺其戶，闃其無人，自藏也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十六卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">旅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>旅：小亨，旅貞吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：旅，小亨，柔得中乎外，而順乎剛，止而麗乎明，是以小亨，旅貞吉也。\n　　　旅之時義大矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山上有火，旅；君子以明慎用刑，而不留獄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：旅瑣瑣，斯其所取災。\n象曰：旅瑣瑣，志窮災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：旅即次，懷其資，得童僕貞。\n象曰：得童僕貞，終無尤也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：旅焚其次，喪其童僕，貞厲。\n象曰：旅焚其次，亦以傷矣。以旅與下，其義喪也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：旅于處，得其資斧，我心不快。\n象曰：旅于處，未得位也。得其資斧，心未快也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：射雉一矢亡，終以譽命。\n象曰：終以譽命，上逮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：鳥焚其巢，旅人先笑後號咷。喪牛于易，凶。\n象曰：以旅在上，其義焚也。喪牛于易，終莫之聞也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十七卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">巽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>巽：小亨，利攸往，利見大人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>彖曰：重巽以申命，剛巽乎中正而志行。柔皆順乎剛，是以小亨，利有攸往，利見大人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：隨風，巽；君子以申命行事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：進退，利武人之貞。\n象曰：進退，志疑也。利武人之貞，志治也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：巽在床下，用史巫紛若，吉無咎。\n象曰：紛若之吉，得中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：頻巽，吝。\n象曰：頻巽之吝，志窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：悔亡，田獲三品。\n象曰：田獲三品，有功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：貞吉悔亡，無不利。無初有終，先庚三日，後庚三日，吉。\n象曰：九五之吉，位正中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：巽在床下，喪其資斧，貞凶。\n象曰：巽在床下，上窮也。喪其資斧，正乎，凶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十八卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">兌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>兌：亨，利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：兌，說也。剛中而柔外，說以利貞，是以順乎天而應乎人。\n　　　說以先民，民忘其勞；說以犯難，民忘其死；說之大，民勸矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：麗澤，兌；君子以朋友講習。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：和兌，吉。\n象曰：和兌之吉，行未疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：孚兌，吉，悔亡。\n象曰：孚兌之吉，信志也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：來兌，凶。\n象曰：來兌之凶，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：商兌，未寧，介疾有喜。\n象曰：九四之喜，有慶也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：孚于剝，有厲。\n象曰：孚于剝，位正當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：引兌。\n象曰：上六引兌，未光也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第五十九卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">渙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>渙：亨。王假有廟，利涉大川，利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：渙，亨。剛來而不窮，柔得位乎外而上同。王假有廟，王乃在中也。\n　　　利涉大川，乘木有功也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：風行水上，渙；先王以享于帝立廟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：用拯馬壯，吉。\n象曰：初六之吉，順也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：渙奔其機，悔亡。\n象曰：渙奔其機，得願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：渙其躬，無悔。\n象曰：渙其躬，志在外也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：渙其群，元吉。渙有丘，匪夷所思。\n象曰：渙其群，元吉；光大也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：渙汗其大號，渙王居，無咎。\n象曰：王居無咎，正位也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：渙其血，去逖出，無咎。\n象曰：渙其血，遠害也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第 六十 卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>節：亨。苦節不可貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：節，亨，剛柔分，而剛得中。苦節不可貞，其道窮也。\n　　　說以行險，當位以節，中正以通。天地節而四時成，節以制度，不傷財，不害民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上有水，節；君子以制數度，議德行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：不出戶庭，無咎。\n象曰：不出戶庭，知通塞也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：不出門庭，凶。\n象曰：不出門庭，失時極也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：不節若，則嗟若，無咎。\n象曰：不節之嗟，又誰咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：安節，亨。\n象曰：安節之亨，承上道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：甘節，吉；往有尚。\n象曰：甘節之吉，居位中也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：苦節，貞凶，悔亡。\n象曰：苦節貞凶，其道窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第六十一卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">中孚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>中孚：豚魚，吉，利涉大川，利貞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：中孚，柔在內而剛得中。說而巽，孚，乃化邦也。豚魚吉，信及豚魚也。\n　　　利涉大川，乘木舟虛也。中孚以利貞，乃應乎天也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：澤上有風，中孚；君子以議獄緩死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：虞吉，有他不燕。\n象曰：初九虞吉，志未變也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：鳴鶴在陰，其子和之，我有好爵，吾與爾靡之。\n象曰：其子和之，中心願也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：得敵，或鼓或罷，或泣或歌。\n象曰：可鼓或罷，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：月幾望，馬匹亡，無咎。\n象曰：馬匹亡，絕類上也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：有孚攣如，無咎。\n象曰：有孚攣如，位正當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：翰音登于天，貞凶。\n象曰：翰音登于天，何可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第六十二卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">小過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>小過：亨，利貞，可小事，不可大事。飛鳥遺之音，不宜上宜下，大吉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：小過，小者過而亨也。過以利貞，與時行也。柔得中，是以小事吉也。\n　　　剛失位而不中，是以不可大事也。\n　　　有飛鳥之象焉，有飛鳥遺之音，不宜上宜下，大吉；上逆而下順也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：山上有雷，小過；君子以行過乎恭，喪過乎哀，用過乎儉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：飛鳥以凶。\n象曰：飛鳥以凶，不可如何也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：過其祖，遇其妣；不及其君，遇其臣；無咎。\n象曰：不及其君，臣不可過也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：弗過防之，從或戕之，凶。\n象曰：從或戕之，凶如何也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：無咎，弗過遇之。往厲必戒，勿用永貞。\n象曰：弗過遇之，位不當也。往厲必戒，終不可長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：密雲不雨，自我西郊，公弋取彼在穴。\n象曰：密雲不雨，已上也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：弗遇過之，飛鳥離之，凶，是謂災眚。\n象曰：弗遇過之，已亢也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第六十三卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">既濟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>既濟：亨，小利貞，初吉終亂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：既濟，亨，小者亨也。利貞，剛柔正而位當也。初吉，柔得中也。\n　　　終止則亂，其道窮也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：水在火上，既濟；君子以思患而預防之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初九：曳其輪，濡其尾，無咎。\n象曰：曳其輪，義無咎也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六二：婦喪其茀，勿逐，七日得。\n象曰：七日得，以中道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九三：高宗伐鬼方，三年克之，小人勿用。\n象曰：三年克之，憊也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六四：繻有衣袽，終日戒。\n象曰：終日戒，有所疑也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九五：東鄰殺牛，不如西鄰之禴祭，實受其福。\n象曰：東鄰殺牛，不如西鄰之時也；實受其福，吉大來也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上六：濡其首，厲。\n象曰：濡其首厲，何可久也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第六十四卦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">未濟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>未濟：亨，小狐汔濟，濡其尾，無攸利。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彖曰：未濟，亨；柔得中也。小狐汔濟，未出中也。濡其尾，無攸利；\n　　　不續終也。雖不當位，剛柔應也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>象曰：火在水上，未濟；君子以慎辨物居方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>初六：濡其尾，吝。\n象曰：濡其尾，亦不知極也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九二：曳其輪，貞吉。\n象曰：九二貞吉，中以行正也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六三：未濟，征凶，利涉大川。\n象曰：未濟征凶，位不當也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>九四：貞吉，悔亡，震用伐鬼方，三年有賞于大國。\n象曰：貞吉悔亡，志行也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>六五：貞吉，無悔，君子之光，有孚，吉。\n象曰：君子之光，其暉吉也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>上九：有孚于飲酒，無咎，濡其首，有孚失是。\n象曰：飲酒濡首，亦不知節也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　天尊地卑，乾坤定矣。卑高以陳，貴賤位矣。動靜有常，剛柔斷矣。\n　　方以類聚，物以群分，吉凶生矣。在天成象，在地成形，變化見矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　是故，剛柔相摩，八卦相盪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　鼓之以雷霆，潤之以風雨，日月運行，一寒一暑。\n　　乾道成男，坤道成女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　乾知大始，坤作成物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　乾以易知，坤以簡能。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易則易知，簡則易從。易知則有親，易從則有功。\n　　有親則可久，有功則可大。可久則賢人之德，可大則賢人之業。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　易簡，而天下之理得矣；天下之理得，而成位乎其中矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第二章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　聖人設卦觀象，繫辭焉而明吉凶，剛柔相推而生變化。\n　　是故，吉凶者，失得之象也。悔吝者，憂虞之象也。變化者，進退之象也。\n　　剛柔者，晝夜之象也。六爻之動，三極之道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，君子所居而安者，易之序也。所樂而玩者，爻之辭也。\n　　是故，君子居則觀其象而玩其辭，動則觀其變而玩其占。\n　　是以自天祐之，吉無不利。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第三章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　彖者，言乎象者也。爻者，言乎變者也。吉凶者，言乎其失得也。\n　　悔吝者，言乎其小疵也。無咎者，善補過也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，列貴賤者，存乎位。齊小大者，存乎卦。辯吉凶者，存乎辭。\n　　憂悔吝者，存乎介。震無咎者，存乎悔。是故，卦有小大，辭有險易。\n　　辭也者，也各指其所之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第四章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　易與天地準，故能彌綸天地之道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　仰以觀於天文，俯以察於地理，是故知幽明之故。原始反終，故知死生之說。\n　　精氣為物，游魂為變，是故知鬼神之情狀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  與天地相似，故不違。知周乎萬物，而道濟天下，故不過。<br>\n\n  旁行而不流，樂天知命，故不憂。安土敦乎仁，故能愛。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　範圍天地之化而不過，曲成萬物而不遺，通乎晝夜之道而知，\n　　故神無方而易無體。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第五章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　一陰一陽之謂道，繼之者善也，成之者性也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　仁者見之謂之仁，知者見之謂之知，百姓日用而不知，故君子之道鮮矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　顯諸仁，藏諸用，鼓萬物而不與聖人同憂，盛德大業至矣哉！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　富有之謂大業，日新之謂盛德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　生生之謂易，成象之謂乾，效法之謂坤，極數知來之謂占，通變之謂事，陰陽不測之謂神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第六章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　夫易，廣矣大矣！以言乎遠，則不御；以言乎邇，則靜而正；\n　　以言乎天地之間，則備矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　夫乾，其靜也專，其動也直，是以大生焉。\n　　夫坤，其靜也翕，其動也辟，是以廣生焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第七章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「易其至矣乎！」夫易，聖人所以崇德而廣業也。知崇禮卑，\n　　　　　　崇效天，卑法地，天地設位，而易行乎其中矣。成性存存，道義之門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第八章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　聖人有以見天下之賾，而擬諸其形容，象其物宜；是故謂之象。\n　　聖人有以見天下之動，而觀其會通，以行其典禮。\n　　繫辭焉，以斷其吉凶；是故謂之爻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　言天下之至賾，而不可惡也。言天下之至動，而不可亂也。\n　　擬之而後言，議之而後動，擬議以成其變化。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「鳴鶴在陰，其子和之，我有好爵，吾與爾靡之。」子曰：「君子居其室，\n　　　出其言，善則千里之外應之，況其邇者乎？居其室，出其言，不善千里之外違之，況其邇者乎？\n　　　言出乎身，加乎民；行發乎邇，見乎遠；言行君子之樞機，\n　　　樞機之發，榮辱之主也。言行，君子之所以動天地也，可不慎乎？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「同人，先號啕而後笑。」子曰：「君子之道，或出或處，或默或語，<br>\n\n   二人同心，其利斷金；同心之言，其臭如蘭。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「初六，藉用白茅，無咎。」子曰：「苟錯諸地而可矣；席用白茅，何咎之有？<br>\n\n   慎之至也。夫茅之為物薄，而用可重也。慎斯術也以往，其無所失矣。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「勞謙君子，有終吉。」子曰：「勞而不伐，有功而不德，厚之至也，<br>\n\n   語以其功下人者也。德言盛，禮言恭，謙也者，致恭以存其位者也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「亢龍有悔。」<br>\n\n   子曰：「貴而無位，高而無民，賢人在下位而無輔，<br>\n\n       是以動而有悔也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「不出戶庭，無咎。」子曰：「亂之所生也，則言語以為階。君不密，則失臣；\n　　　臣不密，則失身；幾事不密，則害成；是以君子慎密而不出也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「作易者其知盜乎？易曰：『負且乘，致寇至。』負也者，小人之事也；\n　　　　　　小人而乘君子之器，盜思奪矣！上慢下暴，盜思伐之矣！慢藏誨盜，冶容誨淫，\n　　　　　　易曰：『負且乘，致寇至。』盜之招也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第九章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　天一地二，天三地四，天五地六，天七地八，天九地十。天數五，地數五，\n　　五位相得而各有合。天數二十有五，地數三十，凡天地之數，五十有五，\n　　此所以成變化而行鬼神也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　大衍之數五十，其用四十有九。分而為二以象兩，掛一以象三，\n　　揲之以四以象四時，歸奇於扐以象閏，五歲再閏。故再扐而後掛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  乾之策，二百一十有六。坤之策，百四十有四。凡三百有六十，當期之日。<br>\n\n  二篇之策，萬有一千五百二十，當萬物之數也。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  是故，四營而成易，十有八變而成卦，八卦而小成。引而伸之，觸類而長之，<br>\n\n  天下之能事畢矣。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　顯道神德行，是故可與酬酢，可與祐神矣。子曰：「知變化之道者，\n　　其知神之所為乎！」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第十章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易有聖人之道四焉，以言者尚其辭，以動者尚其變，以制器者尚其象，\n　　以卜筮者尚其占。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是以君子將有為也，將有行也，問焉而以言，其受命也如嚮，\n　　無有遠近幽深，遂知來物。\n　　非天下之至精，其孰能與於此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　參伍以變，錯綜其數，通其變，遂成天地之文；極其數，遂定天下之象。\n　　非天下之致變，其孰能與於此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易無思也，無為也，寂然不動，感而遂通天下之故。\n　　非天下之至神，其孰能與於此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　夫易，聖人之所以極深而研幾也。惟深也，故能通天下之志；\n　　惟幾也，故能成天下之務；惟神也，故不疾而速，不行而至。\n　　子曰：「易有聖人之道四焉」者，此之謂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第十一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「夫易何為者也？夫易開物成務，冒天下之道，如斯而已者也。\n　　　　　　是故，聖人以通天下之志，以定天下之業，以斷天下之疑。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，蓍之德，圓而神；卦之德，方以知；六爻之義，易以貢。\n　　聖人以此洗心，退藏於密，吉凶與民同患。神以知來，知以藏往，\n　　其孰能與於此哉！古之聰明睿知神武而不殺者夫？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是以，明於天之道，而察於民之故，是與神物以前民用。\n　　聖人以此齋戒，以神明其德夫！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  是故，闔戶謂之坤；闢戶謂之乾；一闔一闢謂之變；往來不窮謂之通；<br>\n\n  見乃謂之象；形乃謂之器；制而用之，謂之法；利用出入，民咸用之，謂之神。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，易有太極，是生兩儀，兩儀生四象，四象生八卦，八卦定吉凶，\n　　吉凶生大業。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，法象莫大乎天地；變通莫大乎四時；懸象著明莫大乎日月；\n　　崇高莫大乎富貴；備物致用，立成器以為天下利，莫大乎聖人；探賾索隱，\n　　鉤深致遠，以定天下之吉凶，成天下之亹亹者，莫大乎蓍龜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，天生神物，聖人則之。天地變化，聖人效之。天垂象，見吉凶，\n　　聖人象之。河出圖，洛出書，聖人則之。易有四象，所以示也。\n　　繫辭焉，所以告也。定之以吉凶，所以斷也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>《易經﹒繫辭上傳》 第十二章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  易曰：「自天祐之，吉無不利。」<br>\n\n  子曰：「祐者助也。天之所助者，順也；人之所助者，信也。履信思乎順，<br>\n\n      又以尚賢也。是以自天祐之，吉無不利也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  子曰：「書不盡言，言不盡意；然則聖人之意，其不可見乎？」<br>\n\n  子曰：「聖人立象以盡意，設卦以盡情偽，繫辭焉以盡其言，變而通之以盡利，<br>\n\n      鼓之舞之以盡神。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  乾坤其易之縕邪？乾坤成列，而易立乎其中矣。乾坤毀，則無以見易；<br>\n\n  易不可見，則乾坤或幾乎息矣。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，形而上者謂之道；形而下者謂之器；化而裁之謂之變；推而行之謂之通；\n　　舉而錯之天下之民，謂之事業。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，夫象，聖人有以見天下之賾，而擬諸形容，象其物宜，是故謂之象。\n　　聖人有以見天下之動，而觀其會通，以行其典禮，繫辭焉，以斷其吉凶，\n　　是故謂之爻。極天下之賾者，存乎卦；鼓天下之動者，存乎辭；化而裁之，存乎變；\n　　推而行之，存乎通；神而明之，存乎其人；默而成之，不言而信，存乎德行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>第一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　八卦成列，象在其中矣。因而重之，爻在其中矣。剛柔相推，變在其中矣。\n　　繫辭焉而命之，動在其中矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　吉凶悔吝者，生乎動者也。剛柔者，立本者也。變通者，趣時者也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　吉凶者，貞勝者也。天地之道，貞觀者也。日月之道，貞明者也。\n　　天下之動，貞夫一者也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　夫乾，確然示人易矣。夫坤，隤然示人簡矣。爻也者，效此者也。\n　　象也者，像此者也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　爻象動乎內，吉凶見乎外，功業見乎變，聖人之情見乎辭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　天地之大德曰生，聖人之大寶曰位。何以守位曰仁。何以聚人曰財。\n　　理財正辭，禁民為非曰義。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第二章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　古者包羲氏之王天下也，仰則觀象於天，俯則觀法於地，觀鳥獸之文，與地之宜，\n　　近取諸身，遠取諸物，於是始作八卦，以通神明之德，以類萬物之情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　作結繩而為網罟，以佃以漁，蓋取諸離。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　包羲氏沒，神農氏作，斲木為耜，揉木為耒，耒耨之利，以教天下，蓋取諸益。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　日中為市，致天下之民，聚天下之貨，交易而退，各得其所，蓋取諸噬嗑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　神農氏沒，黃帝、堯、舜氏作，通其變，使民不倦，神而化之，使民宜之。\n　　易窮則變，變則通，通則久。是以自天祐之，吉無不利，\n　　黃帝、堯、舜，垂衣裳而天下治，蓋取諸乾坤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　刳木為舟，剡木為楫，舟楫之利，以濟不通，致遠以利天下，蓋取諸渙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　服牛乘馬，引重致遠，以利天下，蓋取諸隨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　重門擊柝，以待暴客，蓋取諸豫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　斷木為杵，掘地為臼，臼杵之利，萬民以濟，蓋取諸小過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　弦木為弧，剡木為矢，弧矢之利，以威天下，蓋取諸睽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　上古穴居而野處，後世聖人易之以宮室，上棟下宇，以待風雨，蓋取諸大壯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　古之葬者，厚衣之以薪，葬之中野，不封不樹，喪期無數，後世聖人易之以棺槨，\n　　蓋取諸大過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　上古結繩而治，後世聖人易之以書契，百官以治，萬民以察，蓋取諸夬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第三章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，易者象也。象也者，像也。彖者材也。爻也者，效天下之動也。\n　　是故，吉凶生，而悔吝著也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第四章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　陽卦多陰，陰卦多陽，其故何也？陽卦奇，陰卦耦。其德行何也？\n　　陽一君而二民，君子之道也。陰二君而一民，小人之道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第五章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易曰：「憧憧往來，朋從爾思。」\n　　子曰：「天下何思何慮？天下同歸而殊途，一致而百慮，天下何思何慮？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「日往則月來，月往則日來，日月相推而明生焉。寒往則暑來，暑往則寒來，<br>\n\n   寒暑相推而歲成焉。往者屈也，來者信也，屈信相感而利生焉。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  「尺蠖之屈，以求信也。龍蛇之蟄，以存身也。精義入神，以致用也。<br>\n\n   利用安身，以崇德也。過此以往，未之或知也。窮神知化，德之盛也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  易曰：「困于石，據于蒺藜，入于其宮，不見其妻，凶。」<br>\n\n  子曰：「非所困而困焉，名必辱。非所據而據焉，身必危。<br>\n\n      既辱且危，死期將至，妻其可得見邪？」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  易曰：「公用射隼，于高墉之上，獲之無不利。」<br>\n\n  子曰：「隼者禽也，弓矢者器也，射之者人也。君子藏器於身，待時而動，<br>\n\n      何不利之有？動而不括，是以出而有獲。語成器而動者也。」<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「小人不恥不仁，不畏不義，不見利不勸，不威不懲；\n　　　　　　小懲而大誡，此小人之福也。易曰：『履校滅趾，無咎。』此之謂也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「善不積，不足以成名；惡不積，不足以滅身。小人以小善為無益，而弗為也，\n　　　以小惡而無傷，而弗去也，故惡積而不可掩，罪大而不可解。\n　　　易曰：『履校滅耳，凶。』」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「危者，安其位者也；亡者，保其存者也；亂者，有其治者也。\n　　　　　　是故，君子安而不忘危，存而不忘亡，治而不忘亂；是以，身安而國家可保也。\n　　　　　　易曰：『其亡其亡，繫于苞桑。』」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「德薄而位尊，知小而謀大，力小而任重，鮮不及矣。\n　　易曰：『鼎折足，覆公餗，其形渥，凶』言不勝其任也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「知幾其神乎，君子上交不諂，下交不瀆，其知幾乎？\n　　　　　　幾者，動之微，吉之先見者也，君子見幾而作，不俟終日，\n　　　　　　易曰：『介於石，不終日，貞吉』，介如石焉，寧用終日，斷可識矣。\n　　　　　　君子知微知彰，知柔知剛，萬夫之望。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「顏氏之子，其殆庶幾乎，有不善未嘗不知，知之未嘗復行也，\n　　易曰：『不遠復，無祇悔，元吉』」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　「天地絪縕，萬物化醇。男女構精，萬物化生。易曰：『三人行，則損一人；\n　　　一人行，則得其友。』言致一也。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「君子安其身而後動，易其心而後語，定其交而後求。君子修此三者，\n　　　　　　故全也。危以動，則民不與也；懼以語，則民不應也；無交而求，則民不與也。\n　　　　　　莫之與，則傷之者至矣。易曰：『莫益之，或擊之，立心勿恆，凶。』」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第六章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「乾坤其易之門邪？乾陽物也，坤陰物也。陰陽合德，而剛柔有體，\n　　　　　　以體天地之撰，以通神明之德。其稱名也，雜而不越。於稽其類，其衰世之意邪？」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　子曰：「夫易，彰往而察來，而微顯闡幽，開而當名，辨物正言，斷辭則備矣。\n　　　　　　其稱名也小，其取類也大，其旨遠，其辭文，其言曲而中，其事肆而隱，\n　　　　　　因貳以濟民行，以明失得之報。」</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第七章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　易之興也，其於中古乎？作易者，其有憂患乎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　是故，履，德之基也；謙，德之柄也；復，德之本也；恆，德之固也；\n　　損，德之修也；益，德之裕也；困，德之辨也；井，德之地也；巽，德之制也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  履，和而至；謙，尊而光；復，小而辨於物；恆，雜而不厭；損，先難而後易；<br>\n\n  益，長裕而不設；困，窮而通；井，居其所而遷；巽，稱而隱。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　履，以和行；謙，以制禮；復，以自知；恆，以一德；損，以遠害；\n　　益，以興利；困，以寡怨；井，以辨義；巽，以行權。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第八章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易之為書也，不可遠；為道也，屢遷。變動不居，周流六虛，上下無常，\n　　剛柔相易，不可為典要，唯變所適。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　其出入以度，外內使知懼，又明於憂患與故，無有師保，如臨父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　初率其辭，而揆其方，既有典常。苟非其人，道不虛行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第九章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　易之為書也，原始要終，以為質也。六爻相雜，唯其時物也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　其初難知，其上易知，本末也。初辭擬之，卒成之終。若夫雜物撰德，\n　　辨是與非，則非其中爻不備。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　噫！亦要存亡吉凶，則居可知矣。知者觀其彖辭，則思過半矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　二與四位，同功而異位，其善不同，二多譽，四多懼，近也。\n　　柔之為道，不利遠者，其要無咎，其用柔中也。\n　　三與五，同功而異位，三多凶，五多功，貴賤之等也。其柔危，其剛勝邪？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第十章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易之為書也，廣大悉備，有天道焉，有人道焉，有地道焉。\n　　兼三才而兩之，故六；六者非它也，三才之道也。\n　　道有變動，故曰爻；爻有等，故曰物；物相雜，故曰文；文不當，故吉凶生焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第十一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　易之興也，其當殷之末世，周之盛德邪？當文王與紂之事邪？是故其辭危。\n　　危者使平，易者使傾，其道甚大，百物不廢。\n　　懼以終始，其要無咎，此之謂易之道也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒繫辭下傳》 第十二章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　夫乾，天下之至健也，德行恆易以知險。\n　　夫坤，天下之至順也，德行恆簡以知阻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　能說諸心，能研諸侯之慮，定天下之吉凶，成天下之亹亹者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　是故，變化云為，吉事有祥，象事知器，占事未來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　天地設位，聖人成能，人謀鬼謀，百姓與能。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　八卦以象告，爻彖以情言，剛柔雜居，而吉凶可見矣！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  變動以利言，吉凶以情遷。是故，愛惡相攻而吉凶生；遠近相取而悔吝生，<br>\n\n  情偽相感而利害生。<br>\n\n  凡易之情，近而不相得則凶；或害之，悔且吝。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　將叛者，其辭慚，中心疑者其辭枝，吉人之辭寡，躁人之辭多，\n　　誣善之人其辭游，失其守者其辭屈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　昔者，聖人之作易也，幽贊神明而生蓍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　參天兩地，而倚數，觀變於陰陽，而立卦；\n　　發揮於剛柔，而生爻；和順於道德，而理於義；\n　　窮理盡性，以至於命。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第二章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　昔者聖人之作易也，將以順性命之理。是以立天之道，曰陰與陽；\n　　立地之道，曰柔與剛；立人之道，曰仁與義。兼三才而兩之，故易六畫而成卦。\n　　分陰分陽，迭用柔剛，故易六位而成章。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第三章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　天地定位，山澤通氣，雷風相薄，水火不相射，八卦相錯，數往者順，知來者逆；\n　　是故，易逆數也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第四章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　雷以動之，風以散之，雨以潤之，日以烜之，\n　　艮以止之，兌以說之，乾以君之，坤以藏之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第五章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  帝出乎震，齊乎巽，相見乎離，致役乎坤，說言乎兌，戰乎乾，<br>\n\n  勞乎坎，成言乎艮。<br>\n\n  萬物出乎震，震東方也。齊乎巽，巽東南也，齊也者，言萬物之潔齊也。<br>\n\n  離也者，明也，萬物皆相見，南方之卦也，聖人南面而聽天下，嚮明而治，<br>\n\n  蓋取諸此也。<br>\n\n  坤也者地也，萬物皆致養焉，故曰致役乎坤。兌正秋也，萬物之所說也，故曰說；<br>\n\n  言乎兌。戰乎乾，乾西北之卦也，言陰陽相薄也。坎者水也，正北方之卦也，<br>\n\n  勞卦也，萬物之所歸也，故曰勞乎坎。艮東北之卦也，萬物之所成，<br>\n\n  終而所成始也，故曰成言乎艮。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第六章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　神也者，妙萬物而為言者也。動萬物者，莫疾乎雷；橈萬物者，莫疾乎風；\n　　燥萬物者，莫熯乎火；說萬物者，莫說乎澤；潤萬物者，莫潤乎水；\n　　終萬物始萬物者，莫盛乎艮。故水火相逮，雷風不相悖，山澤通氣，\n　　然後能變化，既成萬物也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>《易經﹒說卦傳》 第七章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　乾，健也；坤，順也；震，動也；巽，入也；\n　　坎，陷也；離，麗也；艮，止也；兌，說也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第八章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　乾為馬，坤為牛，震為龍，巽為雞，\n　　坎為豕，離為雉，艮為狗，兌為羊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第九章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　乾為首，坤為腹，震為足，巽為股，\n　　坎為耳，離為目，艮為手，兌為口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第十章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　乾天也，故稱父，坤地也，故稱母；\n　　震一索而得男，故謂之長男；巽一索而得女，故謂之長女；\n　　坎再索而得男，故謂之中男；離再索而得女，故謂之中女；\n　　艮三索而得男，故謂之少男；兌三索而得女，故謂之少女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒說卦傳》 第十一章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　乾為天、為圜、為君、為父、為玉、為金、為寒、為冰、\n　　為大赤、為良馬、為老馬、為瘠馬、為駁馬、為木果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>  坤為地、為母、為布、為釜、為吝嗇、為均、為子母牛、<br>\n\n  為大輿、為文、為眾、為柄、其於地也為黑。<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　震為雷、為龍、為玄黃、為敷、為大塗、為長子、為決躁、為蒼筤竹、為萑葦。\n　　其於馬也，為善鳴、為馵足，為的顙。其於稼也，為反生。其究為健，為蕃鮮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　巽為木、為風、為長女、為繩直、為工、為白、為長、為高、為進退、\n　　為不果、為臭。其於人也，為寡髮、為廣顙、為多白眼、為近利市三倍。\n　　其究為躁卦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　坎為水、為溝瀆、為隱伏、為矯輮、為弓輪。\n　　其於人也，為加憂、為心病、為耳痛、為血卦、為赤。\n　　其於馬也，為美脊、為亟心、為下首、為薄蹄、為曳。\n　　其於輿也，為多眚。為通、為月、為盜。其於木也，為堅多心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　離為火、為日、為電、為中女、為甲冑、為戈兵。\n　　其於人也，為大腹，為乾卦。為鱉、為蟹、為蠃、為蚌、為龜。\n　　其於木也，為科上槁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　艮為山、為徑路、為小石、為門闕、為果蓏、為閽寺、為指、為狗、為鼠、\n　　為黔喙之屬。其於木也，為堅多節。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　兌為澤、為少女、為巫、為口舌、為毀折、為附決。\n　　其於地也，為剛鹵。為妾、為羊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒序卦傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　有天地，然後萬物生焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　盈天地之間者，唯萬物，故受之以屯；\n　　屯者盈也，屯者物之始生也。物生必蒙，故受之以蒙；\n　　蒙者蒙也，物之稚也。物稚不可不養也，故受之以需；\n　　需者飲食之道也。飲食必有訟，故受之以訟。\n　　訟必有眾起，故受之以師；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　師者眾也。眾必有所比，故受之以比；\n　　比者比也。比必有所畜也，故受之以小畜。\n　　物畜然後有禮，故受之以履。\n　　履而泰，然後安，故受之以泰；\n　　泰者通也。物不可以終通，故受之以否。\n　　物不可以終否，故受之以同人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　與人同者，物必歸焉，故受之以大有。\n　　有大者不可以盈，故受之以謙。\n　　有大而能謙，必豫，故受之以豫。\n　　豫必有隨，故受之以隨。\n　　以善隨人者，必有事，故受之以蠱；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　蠱者事也。有事而後可大，故受之以臨；\n　　臨者大也。物大然後可觀，故受之以觀。\n　　可觀而後有合，故受之以噬嗑；\n　　嗑者合也。物不可以苟合而已，故受之以賁；\n　　賁者飾也。致飾然後亨則盡矣，故受之以剝；\n　　剝者剝也。物不可以終盡，剝窮上反下，故受之以復。\n　　復則不妄矣，故受之以無妄。\n　　有無妄然後可畜，故受之以大畜。\n　　物畜然後可養，故受之以頤；\n　　頤者養也。不養則不可動，故受之以大過。\n　　物不可以終過，故受之以坎；\n　　坎者陷也。陷必有所麗，故受之以離；離者麗也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　有天地，然後有萬物；有萬物，然後有男女；有男女，然後有夫婦；\n　　有夫婦，然後有父子；有父子然後有君臣；有君臣，然後有上下；\n　　有上下，然後禮儀有所錯。夫婦之道，不可以不久也，故受之以恆；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　恆者久也。物不可以久居其所，故受之以遯；\n　　遯者退也。物不可終遯，故受之以大壯。\n　　物不可以終壯，故受之以晉；\n　　晉者進也。進必有所傷，故受之以明夷；\n　　夷者傷也。傷於外者，必反其家，故受之以家人。\n　　家道窮必乖，故受之以睽；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　睽者乖也。乖必有難，故受之以蹇；\n　　蹇者難也。物不可終難，故受之以解；\n　　解者緩也。緩必有所失，故受之以損；\n　　損而不已，必益，故受之以益。\n　　益而不已，必決，故受之以夬；\n　　夬者決也。決必有所遇，故受之以姤；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　姤者遇也。物相遇而後聚，故受之以萃；\n　　萃者聚也。聚而上者，謂之升，故受之以升。\n　　升而不已，必困，故受之以困。\n　　困乎上者，必反下，故受之以井。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　井道不可不革，故受之以革。\n　　革物者莫若鼎，故受之以鼎。\n　　主器者莫若長子，故受之以震；\n　　震者動也。物不可以終動，止之，故受之以艮；\n　　艮者止也。物不可以終止，故受之以漸；\n　　漸者進也。進必有所歸，故受之以歸妹。\n　　得其所歸者必大，故受之以豐；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　豐者大也。窮大者必失其居，故受之以旅。\n　　旅而無所容，故受之以巽；\n　　巽者入也。入而後說之，故受之以兌；\n　　兌者說也。說而後散之，故受之以渙；\n　　渙者離也。物不可以終離，故受之以節。\n　　節而信之，故受之以中孚。\n　　有其信者，必行之，故受之以小過。\n　　有過物者，必濟，故受之既濟。\n　　物不可窮也，故受之以未濟，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　終焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《易經﹒雜卦傳》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　乾剛，坤柔，比樂，師憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　臨、觀之義，或與或求。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　屯見而不失其居。蒙雜而著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　震起也，艮止也；損益盛衰之始也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　大畜時也。無妄災也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　萃聚，而升不來也。謙輕，而豫怠也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　噬嗑食也，賁無色也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　兌見，而巽伏也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　隨無故也，蠱則飭也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　剝爛也，復反也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　晉晝也，明夷誅也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　井通，而困相遇也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　咸速也，恆久也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　渙離也，節止也；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　解緩也，蹇難也；睽外也，家人內也；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　否泰反其類也。大壯則止，遯則退也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　大有眾也，同人親也；革去故也，鼎取新也；小過過也，中孚信也；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　豐多故，親寡旅也。離上，而坎下也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p>　　小畜寡也，履不處也。需不進也，訟不親也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">　　大過顛也。姤遇也，柔遇剛也。漸女歸，待男行也。\n　　頤養正也，既濟定也。歸妹女之終也。\n　　未濟男之窮也。夬決也，剛決柔也，君子道長，小人道憂也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/cc2a9266ff022725/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-f09fcd twpub-cc2a9266ff022725-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** END OF THE PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK YI JING ***</p></div>"
        },
